text: Heads up to everyone using the :chrome: <#CBBAW6Z3R|community-browser-extension> I am aware of the fact the developer menu is no longer appearing. This was caused by a change HubSpot made to their header. I will try to get a fix into the beta over the weekend for this. We will then try to get it into stable just in time for New Years
Beta build with fix has been pushed. let me know if you want access to the beta. otherwise  as I said stable build should hit around new years
